{
  "name": "Page",
  "summary": "<p>使用 <strong>Item</strong> 方法可访问工作簿的特定页面。</p>\n<p><b class=\"mainheaders\">示例</b></p><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例设置活动工作表页面居中对齐的页眉内容为“Sheet1”。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> objPage = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">PageSetup</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Pages</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    objPage.<span class=\"hljs-property\">CenterHeader</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Text</span> = <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Sheet1&quot;</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例设置 Sheet1 页面右对齐的页眉内容为“Sheet1”，并且显示页眉右对齐的文本内容。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> page = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Sheet1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">PageSetup</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Pages</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    page.<span class=\"hljs-property\">RightHeader</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Text</span> = <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Sheet1&quot;</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">`右页眉的内容：<span class=\"hljs-subst\">${page.RightHeader.Text}</span>`</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
